    "name": "Veggie & Goat Cheese Scramble",
    "category": "breakfast",
    "method": [
      "Heat the olive oil in a non-stick pan over medium heat.",
      "Add the mushrooms and bell pepper and saute for 3-4 minutes until softened.",
      "Add the spinach and cook until just wilted.",
      "Whisk the eggs and pour into the pan, stirring gently as they set.",
      "Once just set, crumble over the hard goat cheese and remove from the heat."
